*samba-2.2.4 (6 May 2002)
  
  6 May 2002; Donny Davies <woodchip@gentoo.org> samba-2.2.4.ebuild,
  smb.conf.example, system-auth-winbind, samba-svc, winbind-init, lmhosts,
